Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:11.77,main title - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,789)\fscx110\fscy110\fad(2450,1000)}— Episode 9.9999 —
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now let's go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're pushing yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not forcing myself or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.92,0:00:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After this let's head to Ikspiari and line up at Gong Cha, then go to Moreru Mignon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Yeah. I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're definitely forcing yourself—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm really not. This is just the first date we've been on in a while, Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.38,0:00:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Still doing your best for me even though you have amnesia, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that said...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:01:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you have amnesia I wish you'd at least remember your girlfriend, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, um... I'm really sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.67,0:01:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.05,0:01:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... It's just so weird that someone so cute suddenly told me they were my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were trying to trick me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, I thought it was some kind of prank—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.04,0:01:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that! What you said before it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Well, yeah, having someone as cute as you tell me you're my girlfriend is—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! I'm your cute girlfriend, Akane, that's me! Yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on... what're we even doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We always do stuff like this. You really don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't {\i1}not{\i0} like it... \NIt's kinda fun, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, while we're talking about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We are, um... our relationship is like, you know, we're lovers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you could call us that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:02:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Uh... Just exactly how close have we been with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "how close"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, I'm not asking for solid answers like how far we've been, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.43,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you seriously don't remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do have amnesia, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying you even forgot something as important as that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember what happened that day? You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened that day...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no, this sounds like it was something really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No no, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not— That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane! ...Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I was just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I was kidding! Of course there's no way I could forget something that important! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, you really scared me! I actually believed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally fooled you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez... You're so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really did forget I would've stabbed you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah... I hope that's just a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So... you do remember what happened that day, right? Honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-oh... This could be bad! Remember! I need to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You do remember what happened that day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Akane, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to hit my head really hard, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? You're scaring me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's fine, just hit me as hard as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! For real! Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only chance is that the impact will jog something in my brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it doesn't, I'll get stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... I'm gonna hit you super hard, ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Please do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually if I don't have anything in my hand I might hold back, mind if I use this jar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Jar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, this jar is made of a kind of metal from outer space called happy cosmonium...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy cosmo—? Uh, well... okay then. Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, here I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm fine, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, totally fine. I actually do remember what happened that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? We don't have to talk about that right now, no need to force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was before summer and on the day we had the ball game rally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We were talking with each other in the classroom during the break, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was before you dyed your hair, Akane. Back when it was long and black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me you were planning to give one of the head bands to a friend who wasn't able to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,While we stood there listening to the loud cheers from the gym...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your black hair was swaying in the wind, just like the curtains in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I realized I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you, Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't there the day of the ball game rally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I haven't changed the length of my hair since I started school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was never black, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? Then who was I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna stab you after all, Hibiki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, wait, wait, Akane! Hold on a sec! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My memory's gotta be messed up—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better be ready, this is gonna hurt a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on... Really?! You really did scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I wasn't gonna stab you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you have to remember every little thing, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make more memories in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...and thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be in your care from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, if I did get stabbed by someone as cute as you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it might just be worth it to see their smile, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, a girlfriend as cute as you—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! Your cute girlfriend, Akane, is gonna stab right through your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, what're we even doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I got no idea!
